## Auto-Computed Results

Final conversion (%) : {{var|final_conv_pct: float}}
Observed rate constant (min<sup>−1</sup>) : {{var|k_obs: float}}
Half-life (min) : {{var|t_half: float}}
Time to 95% conversion (min) : {{var|t_95: float}}
Linear fit quality R<sup>2</sup> : {{var|r2: float}}
QC pass : {{var|qc_pass: bool}}

<details>
<summary>QC criteria</summary>

QC Pass if final conversion ≥ 90% and fit R<sup>2</sup> ≥ 0.95; otherwise QC Fail.

</details>

